{"tid":2309773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丹麥國會議員：許智峯訪問後或轉赴英國","createTime":"2020-12-02T19:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T15:59:26.000Z","uid":227801,"like":162,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"90e2d90c913467b5653a3ffb3de52d3009ee69ce","tid":2309773,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:48:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/36117/%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF-%E4%B8%B9%E9%BA%A5-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7-36117/%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F36117%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF-%25E4%25B8%25B9%25E9%25BA%25A5-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25BA%2587%25E8%25AD%25B7-36117%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=4ca57d25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/36117/%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF-%E4%B8%B9%E9%BA%A5-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7-36117/%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF</a><br />\n有多宗案件在身的民主黨立法會前議員許智峯在保釋期間現身丹麥首都哥本哈根，向許發出訪問邀請的丹麥國會議員Katarina Ammitzboll接受眾新聞查詢時表示，得悉許智峯或在丹麥訪問三日後，將會轉到英國，但目前未見面談及具體計劃。<br />\n<br />\n目前未知許智峯會否在英國尋求庇護，同時傳出許智峯家人周三傍晚離港消息。他在香港時間周四清晨在Facebook更新說，家庭生活無需向公眾交代，自己則按原定行程完成公務外訪，「若有任何新資訊，會再向大家交待」。許智峯本身涉及屯門遊行、立法會內會衝突及國歌法潑異味液體三件事件、共九宗控罪。"},{"pid":"785ad9faba7a985ccb7360d028b7583c1d869c19","tid":2309773,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67ac8ecd23762a0a7f7b830ffae5839cc9384db","tid":2309773,"uid":79117,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:49:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d786dd3bb17096f62d73f719f4d9ee69fd9148e","tid":2309773,"uid":79117,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:50:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4628240c3a6ae5eed8bd6bb81ec9d73b76ae8655","tid